## Common Microsoft 365 connectors reference

| Service | Connector name | Common triggers | Common actions |
|---------|---------------|-----------------|----------------|
| SharePoint | SharePoint | When a file is created, When an item is created/modified | Get items, Create item, Update item, Get file content, Create file |
| Outlook | Office 365 Outlook | When a new email arrives (V3) | Send an email (V2), Get email (V2), Move email |
| Teams | Microsoft Teams | When a new channel message is added | Post message in a chat or channel, Post adaptive card and wait for a response |
| Forms | Microsoft Forms | When a new response is submitted | Get response details |
| Planner | Planner | When a task is assigned to me | Create a task, Update a task, List tasks |
| Dataverse | Microsoft Dataverse | When a row is added/modified/deleted | List rows, Get a row, Add a new row, Update a row |
| OneDrive | OneDrive for Business | When a file is created/modified | Get file content, Create file, Copy file |
| Excel Online | Excel Online (Business) | — | List rows, Add a row, Update a row, Get a row |
| Power Apps | PowerApps (V2) | PowerApps (V2) trigger | Respond to a PowerApp or flow |
| Approvals | Approvals | — | Start and wait for an approval, Create an approval |
| File System | File System (gateway) | When a file is created in a folder | Get file content, Create file, List files in folder |
| HTTP | HTTP | — | HTTP (for REST API calls to any endpoint) |
| AI Builder | AI Builder | — | Extract information from forms, Categorize text, Analyze sentiment |

